Andrea Pirlo has revealed he was wanted by Carlo Ancelotti at #Chelsea in 2010, but the club told him he was too old. <br />
<br />
Pirlo: &ldquo;#Chelsea said that I was very old - 30 years old! And the other time I preferred to come to Juventus. 'For sure it would have been a fantastic experience but I'm happy that I decided to stay in Italy.&quot;

Positive meeting today. Chelsea are ready to release Sarri. His agent Ramadani has left London already.<br />
<br />
{@AlfredoPedulla}
